The paper deals with wireless power transfer (WPT) using energy beamforming, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The use of retrodirective antenna and ambient backscatter also involves system design and control (cs.SY). The proposed training sequence design and analytical modeling of the system can be categorized under machine learning (cs.MM) and learning theory (cs.LG).
